rnalysis.enrichment.EnrichmentProcessing.biotypes¶

EnrichmentProcessing.biotypes(ref: str = 'C:\\Users\\Guy_Teichman\\PycharmProjects\\RNAlysis\\rnalysis\\gene_names_and_biotype.csv')¶

Returns a DataFrame of the biotypes in the gene set and their count.

Parameters

ref – Name of the reference file used to determine biotype. Default is ce11 (included in the package).
